{"tid":11441,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"比人睇高一線好辛苦","createTime":"2016-11-29T09:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T11:11:28.000Z","uid":14758,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02cfa57bea0064d4e3ffad271f0597f036837221","tid":11441,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:46:06.000Z","msg":"明明我冇果種料<br />\n但係人地硬係覺得我高人一等<br />\n搞到我要好care佢地點諗<br />\n挑戰者輸比冠軍，啲人會覺得好正常<br />\n但係冠軍只要輸一次就成千古恨<br />\n<br />\n我仲要係比人睇高一線既冠軍<br />\n頻頻輸比挑戰者令我覺得無地自容<br />\n我到底係度做緊乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0f4ab027863158a03813d7d5cbb98c687fded1","tid":11441,"uid":3987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:50:01.000Z","msg":"最少好過班地底泥先啦"},{"pid":"1c03cba95e4b02c4b8390ef95486ee33ba887841","tid":11441,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:00:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最少好過班地底泥先啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你明唔明白feel到人地心入面講<br />\n「車，乜得咁多架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n果種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d15b88796026bcf0724453da0d9597f4db7e6d","tid":11441,"uid":15686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:02:08.000Z","msg":"有實力先會比人睇高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n信下自己啦"},{"pid":"da174f19a34b1bdc3047496eb74837ff1286f091","tid":11441,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:03:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f97c112d9cf538d49d95f461b4f0ef83e85bb3f3","tid":11441,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:04:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有實力先會比人睇高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n信下自己啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded8381d61f005a050a49ec81963eb440a5c4b02","tid":11441,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:07:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我明，成日比人話乜哥乜哥<br />\n讀書就話無難到你既<br />\n運動就話，我睇你以為好勁，點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我屌，我有春話過我乜都識咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n姐係好似你走去一個叫nba訓練班既野<br />\n學左幾年都輸比街場挑你機果啲中學雞<br />\n仲要啲fd拉哂大隊黎睇果種感覺"},{"pid":"2c709ef6aa088a63a538881fb81d5d1ff0eda124","tid":11441,"uid":623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:36:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我明，成日比人話乜哥乜哥<br />\n讀書就話無難到你既<br />\n運動就話，我睇你以為好勁，點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我屌，我有春話過我乜都識咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩出來社會？叫你乜哥乜哥一家係睇起你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9612fab53ef210e9d9128aa4ab288a3f4e8d105","tid":11441,"uid":16323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:51:20.000Z","msg":"無人睇過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e4de523df8c847aa18e2a7ebd69975a3516ffa","tid":11441,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:58:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無人睇過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好好珍惜以下犯上既機會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ce75aae9867aa2cf32f879ee757f20a7b915f5","tid":11441,"uid":7267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:02:31.000Z","msg":"咁點解你會俾人睇高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583b95353b4083c8cbeadf1a20210213a377383d","tid":11441,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:11:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁點解你會俾人睇高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你當係你去學英文學左好多年<br />\n但係唔識用口同鬼佬講野<br />\n你啲親戚朋友就當你神咁拜<br />\n有一個係外國浸過一兩年咸水識溝通既勁過你<br />\n就即刻踩到你地底泥果種感覺"}]}